You can use SAPLink, to install CT.
Link to user documentation - https://wiki.scn.sap.com/wiki/display/ABAP/SAPlink+User+Documentation
Initial namespace - ZBOBF*
Manual part of installation:
Start transaction SE93 and create transaction ZBOBF_TRACKER_CONFIG as Transaction with parameters(parameter transaction).
	- Default value for transaction: SE16
	- Default parameters:
		Name of screen field: DATABROWSE-TABLENAME, Value: ZBOBF_D_TRACK
		Name of screen field: CALLING_TRANSACTION, Value: X
	Activate, assign ZBOBF_TRACKER_CONFIG to package ZBOBF_TRACKER and leave the transaction.
